## Tone Adaptation Workflow

- [ ] 1. Identify the source copy and its current tone
- [ ] 2. Define the target tone and context
- [ ] 3. Adapt vocabulary, sentence structure, and style
- [ ] 4. Maintain the core message while shifting delivery
- [ ] 5. Review for consistency with brand voice

## Key Inputs
- Source Copy: {{source_copy}}
- Source Tone: {{source_tone}}
- Target Tone: {{target_tone}}
- Target Context: {{target_context}}
